  "summary": "n8n-nodes-final-mile ships a reverse shell to 103.27.109.184:8895 on module load",
  "details": "The package main (index.js) is a self-executing IIFE that, on require/import, opens a TCP socket to the hardcoded remote host 103.27.109.184 on port 8895 and pipes the stdio of spawned /bin/bash -i and /bin/sh -i interactive shells through that socket. Loading this n8n community node hands the remote host interactive command execution on the installer's machine. The behavior is unrelated to the advertised 'final mile delivery' n8n node purpose.",
